[{"id":"4d1a52a8e38d65e6c78e424da49fd56b","from":"image32","from_email":"support@image32.com","to":"jeffrey","to_list":[{"name":"jeffrey","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"image32 Product Update","date":"2015-07-07T21:43:55.000Z","formatted_date":"Jul 7, 2015","formatted_time":"9:43 PM","body":"Hi jeffrey,\n\nIt's time for another product update from image32. We've been listening to our customers and adding new features to help make image32 more useful. Here are just a few of the new features we're rolling out...\n\n- Localizer lines in the viewer\n- Four window layout option\n- Improved support for mobile browsers\n- Improved support for DICOM Structured Reports (SR)\n- Support for larger file attachments\n- Improved performance over low-bandwidth networks\n\nWe're rolling out these features over the next few days. If you want to see a sneak peak, go here and login with your regular username and password: http://image32.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=315fa6a443&e=d239b5474d\n\nWe hope you find many of the above improvements useful. Please let us know what else we can do to make image32 work better for you.\n\nThanks,\nThe image32 team\n\nsupport@image32.com (mailto:support@image32.com)\nhttp://image32.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=2471b31d08&e=d239b5474d (http://image32.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=f334cd9859&e=d239b5474d)\n\n============================================================\nCopyright \u00a9 2015 Interconnect Medical, Inc., All rights reserved.\n You are receiving this email because you are a registered user of image32.\n\nOur mailing address is:\nInterconnect Medical, Inc.\n1149 Chestnut Street\nSuite 10\nMenlo Park, CA 94025\nUSA\n** unsubscribe from this list (http://image32.us6.list-manage.com/unsubscribe?u=1faec27b59029d1114f8d0e19&id=4c2c2f7b6c&e=d239b5474d&c=244452dfe9)\n** update subscription preferences (http://image32.us6.l